{"tid":311410,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該所有爛面JJ入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-07-06T14:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T03:50:16.000Z","uid":7703,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e313e68f892c07a04a1554e0aab8a868cafc6d93","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:54:56.000Z","msg":"如果想改善皮膚問題可以試下以上步驟<br />\n<br />\n首先買一支洗面奶 or 洗面梘 本人油面加敏感性皮膚 鍾意洗面梘，天然得嚟好清爽 唔會冇哂所有面油同冇咁多化學野 <br />\n<br />\n洗面習慣 「千祈唔好用洗巾洗臉，用手掌洗」<br />\n洗巾洗好易磨損塊臉 磨損之後會發炎 生暗瘡 紅腫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後上 爽膚水 冇乜牌子介紹 自己試下試下就知自己鐘意乜 如果敏感性皮膚可以搵下邊啲有洋甘菊成份嘅抗敏爽膚水 爽膚水嘅作用係收毛孔 同恢復肌膚表面嘅酸碱值 <br />\n<br />\n最後搽返啲cream 最好用一啲有保濕嘅面霜 我用緊nivea 好好用 又平又多 唔立 <br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/06/224949_b32017d33f99ce0f28132950e11033f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F06%2F224949_b32017d33f99ce0f28132950e11033f3.jpg&h=70675930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCream對皮膚好緊要千祈覺得自己塊好油所以唔搽cream ，出油係因為塊面覺得冇油先會不停出油 「例如你用完洗面奶唔搽cream出咗街一定出事」千萬記得搽保濕面霜<br />\n<br />\n如果出街搽咗防曬任何有「spa」or 「Pa」30+至50+ 嘅產品 包括BB cream 都要用卸妝水 清潔之後再上「洗面奶 爽膚水 保濕cream 」<br />\n<br />\n另外每三至四日做一次磨砂 磨砂方面 如果你塊面又紅又腫月球表面千祈唔好用有細粒砂狀 要用去角質好似捽完似擦子膠碎個隻 輕力<br />\n<br />\n最後一日or兩日換枕頭袋 懶可以鋪毛巾 <br />\n<br />\n記住 洗臉用奶or梘 之後爽膚水 最後搽cream 一早起身一次 出街一次 沖完涼一次 訓覺一次 不停loop <br />\n得閒full下mask 啦 <br />\n<br />\n如果太嚴重就睇醫生啦 不過以上skincare 睇唔睇都要做"},{"pid":"ea3294bc06b31bfd33c36ad1bb8431a9ef422e6c","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35753804cec087cc5db16ec5a795ed84b114aeb8","tid":311410,"uid":124741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"你個隻nivea係咪普通萬寧個D都有"},{"pid":"584ca4363c37df3c6c6b35f1223351fc0f4b8105","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:09:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個隻nivea係咪普通萬寧個D都有</blockquote><br />\n係呀"},{"pid":"08c2cf0665018d7174442b54a10d6e422847645a","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"75392de60d92a39e62d32f8a9495a69cb928a2ac","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbea5920005b369780c88d02ba9c89612010a630","tid":311410,"uid":35317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:41:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"eb2b48f3e35775dad56f4833cddf98a268a371a5","tid":311410,"uid":57615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:02:29.000Z","msg":"平時泥mask有無必要？"},{"pid":"4a85e1321271b03229e205577d0a790340fb01a6","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:12:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時泥mask有無必要？</blockquote><br />\n得閒咪做下囉 mask 每一隻mask都有唔同效果 通頂夜訓後上保濕mask 會比較明顯有用 美白，去暗瘡要keep住 4～5次先睇得出效果  <br />\n必要就因人而異嘅 貪靚咪有囉<br />\n<br />\n另外如果用美白 or 去暗瘡 mask 出街搽防曬效果會好好多 不過返屋企記得用卸妝水"},{"pid":"ee7b53654d0a7aef5f36af2d2fa111d4ec158af7","tid":311410,"uid":61678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:14:26.000Z","msg":"如果已經係月球係咪冇得搞"},{"pid":"fa3ebbc8981d787341f54327d46c217b016c2ecf","tid":311410,"uid":118357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"有無邊款去角質好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3460318211825e00186786b32a9bcc8d19de807","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果已經係月球係咪冇得搞</blockquote><br />\n一係keep住努力磨沙 保濕  用去暗瘡mask 防曬 總有一日你會有平滑的肌膚 <br />\n<br />\n一係課金睇皮膚醫生激光磨皮，磨完都要繼續做好skincare"},{"pid":"c7d15aa5a0e353e6afc55d67585288c855eaf94a","tid":311410,"uid":70192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"爛面撚留名"},{"pid":"41b6915bae47dd49b2fd9435ebe78379348c92c5","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無邊款去角質好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n覺得隻隻差唔多反正捽完都會洗 接觸時間比較短去到乾淨就得 建議皮膚易過敏 皮膚薄用凝膠去角質  女仔之類"},{"pid":"2095247d6acf63e6dbae7071cb90b3bdd050e367","tid":311410,"uid":57615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時泥mask有無必要？</blockquote><br />\n得閒咪做下囉 mask 每一隻mask都有唔同效果 通頂夜訓後上保濕mask 會比較明顯有用 美白，去暗瘡要keep住 4～5次先睇得出效果  <br />\n必要就因人而異嘅 貪靚咪有囉<br />\n<br />\n另外如果用美白 or 去暗瘡 mask 出街搽防曬效果會好好多 不過返屋企記得用卸妝水</blockquote><br />\n好詳細thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb01c57839e6ccc0420ee9b79c2a13ff56170a68","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平時泥mask有無必要？</blockquote><br />\n得閒咪做下囉 mask 每一隻mask都有唔同效果 通頂夜訓後上保濕mask 會比較明顯有用 美白，去暗瘡要keep住 4～5次先睇得出效果  <br />\n必要就因人而異嘅 貪靚咪有囉<br />\n<br />\n另外如果用美白 or 去暗瘡 mask 出街搽防曬效果會好好多 不過返屋企記得用卸妝水</blockquote><br />\n好詳細thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  幫你推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我果啲比較係基本skincare ，如果話有咩特別產品推介我又up唔出 反正都係果啲牌子 行過莎莎平就買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc77d6ea984a12533297aa7f5e2ec65dee6d26b6","tid":311410,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:56:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"98c4b56073dbf7163bd37507eae4979b573ccddc","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0bcf952bbbc221692fa12f118c7f450d7939f9d","tid":311410,"uid":92016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:18:58.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"c6d964ceaeb4114f132c33623b2495bcbefca00f","tid":311410,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9d6963742cbc8b8e3db9158c54af34b9d53fe7","tid":311410,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:21:30.000Z","msg":"出街點都要搽防曬"},{"pid":"9ea1b33dbe7cbea19b242868d6334493232fa600","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出街點都要搽防曬</blockquote><br />\n另外如果出街覺得又要搽防曬又搽保濕cream好麻煩就可以買「日霜」大部分嘅日霜都有防曬功效 咁就唔洗一次搽兩隻唔同產品咁麻煩 不過返到屋企都要用卸妝水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af600a232c1590292f49768a781a4542692564a9","tid":311410,"uid":7703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T13:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出街點都要搽防曬</blockquote><br />\n另外如果出街覺得又要搽防曬又搽保濕cream好麻煩就可以買「日霜」大部分嘅日霜都有防曬功效 咁就唔洗一次搽兩隻唔同產品咁麻煩 不過返到屋企都要用卸妝水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一返屋企直接用卸妝綿+水 抹一抹 之後洗面奶or梘 然後上爽膚水  最後上保濕cream"},{"pid":"b39da2aa047c0f1fbbd73509d2c698558cf17122","tid":311410,"uid":67895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"樓主嘅理論不適用於所有人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個方法我做左3年，<br />\n成日臨好又爆過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲要爆一粒就成面爆晒<br />\n之後跟人肌斷食，淨用清水洗面<br />\n介晒所有護膚品就冇再爆過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始會乾到仆街，但半個月後，<br />\n皮膚識自己調節返油份，唔會乾唔會油，好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：極乾性皮膚"},{"pid":"002ec153c271f0e7103b79fee6d0af3f0fccb08f","tid":311410,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}